history.content:
We're Cloud at California, and we're bringing cloud education and industry cloud experience to UC Berkeley. Whether you have no experience with cloud or programming, or you're a seasoned developer, Cloud at California is for you!

Have no idea what the cloud is, but sounds interesting? We have an education branch that teaches you all you need to know about cloud technologies, allow you to progress as a cloud developer, and receive multiple AWS certifications. Already have experience with cloud? Join our consulting and development branch where you'll get even more hands-on cloud development experience working on high-impact projects with growing startups.

Applications are due September 10th, Thursday at midnight, and can be found here: https://forms.gle/H65JhJAdgukdpTCr9.

Infosession 1: Wednesday, September 2nd, 8-9 PM PST

https://www.facebook.com/events/627821388117309/

Infosession 2: Thursday, September 3rd, 8-9 PM PST

https://www.facebook.com/events/359196708442140/

Meet & Greet: Tuesday, September 8th, 7:30-9 PM PST

https://www.facebook.com/events/225579788869300/

Visit our website https://cloudatcal.org/ or our Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/cloud.at.cal for more information.
